  |Ah8=8. [[:en:Prince Andrew of Greece and Denmark|Prince Andrew of Greece and Denmark]] |Ah9=9. [[:en:Princess Alice of Battenberg|Princess Alice of Battenberg]]
  |Ah10=10. [[:en:George VI|George VI of the United Kingdom]] |Ah11=11. [[:en:Queen Elizabeth The Queen Mother|Lady Elizabeth Bowes-Lyon]]
  |Ah12=12. [[:en:Albert Spencer, 7th Earl Spencer|Albert Spencer, 7th Earl Spencer]]  |Ah13=13. [[:en:Cynthia Spencer, Countess Spencer|Lady Cynthia Hamilton]]
  |Ah14=14. [[:en:Maurice Roche, 4th Baron Fermoy|Maurice Roche, 4th Baron Fermoy]]  |Ah15=15. [[Ruth Roche, Baroness Fermoy|Ruth Gill]]}}
| | | | |!| | | | | | | |!| | | | | | | | | |!| | | | | | | | |!}}
